		<div class="content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><br /><br /></strong><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">    “声诗润朱弦”音乐会</span></strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong> </strong></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2012</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">10</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">27</span>日晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19:30</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">地点：民族音乐厅</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">主持人：王军（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000;">  
 
</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">一、 </span>女声独唱《五星红旗》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                         天明词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>刘青曲<br /></span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                    </span>《春花秋月》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                     </span>贺东久词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>印青曲<br /></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                               </span>演唱：郑丽红  赵娜</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">二、 </span>女声二重唱《好人好梦》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                              </span>电视剧《空镜子》插曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">   </span>樊孝成词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>宋书华曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                               </span>演唱：赵娜 郑丽红</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">三、  女声独唱《泪的小雨》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                               </span>庄奴词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>彩木雅夫曲<br />                                      《何日君再来》                                                                                             兰玄昭词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>沈毕曲<br />                                      《我是中国人》                                                                                                        刘家昌词曲<br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                            </span>演唱：王紫菲（中华社会救助基金会形象大使）</span></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">四、  琵琶独奏《十面埋伏》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                     </span></span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                   </span>古曲<br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                              </span>演唱：尹秋薇</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">五、 </span></span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: small;"> 女声独唱《玛依拉变奏曲》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                      哈萨克族民歌  胡廷江改编</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                     </span>《我和我的祖国》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                         </span>张藜词 秦咏诚曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                   </span>演唱：吴静（上海国际音乐节获奖者）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">六、女声独唱《长鼓敲起来》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                          李洁思</span>词  <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">金凤浩</span>曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                    </span>《一杯美酒》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                  </span>新疆民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                            </span>演唱：裴长佳（文华奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">七、 </span>女中音独唱《吐鲁番的葡萄熟了》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                           瞿琮词</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  施光南</span>曲</span><br /><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">          </span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                               《祖国我的最爱》                                                                          </span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">              赵明词  印青曲<br /></span>                                                           演唱：王淼</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">八、</span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>女声独唱唱《小河淌水》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                           </span>云南民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000;">                              《欢天喜地》                                                                    乔羽词   戚建波曲</span></span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">                              《青藏高原》                                                                             张千一词曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                              </span>演唱：贾静思（第六届国际音乐节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">九、 </span></span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>京胡独奏《京华气韵》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                                                  </span>吴华曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                 </span>演奏：张学琴</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">十、 </span>女声小合唱《这山唱那山》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                    </span>根据苗侗音乐整理</span></p>
